room_title: Escape room "The Cabin: Fun House Massacre" by Escape Woods in Atlanta

room_description: Can you escape THE FUN HOUSE? One of our most popular games just got a lot bigger and more twisted. In this adventure you and your team will need to escape from a demented fun house and the fun house owner's cabin in the woods to avoid a massacre.
